title: Hermitcraft 8 Episode 17: I'm Back With A SURPRISE!
author: GoodTimesWithScar
description:
Limited Time Swaggon Merch link: https://represent.com/store/goodtimeswithscar

Hermitcraft season 8 episode 17! We start out Ep 17 of Hermitcraft S8 by finding the enormous moon and giving Mumbo his Boatem hat. We meet up with the rest of Boatem and make some company changes and after the meeting, we find a prank from the Big Eyes. I hope you enjoyed the episode and see you in the next one!


Hermitcraft Season 8 playlist: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLSCZsQa9VSCdDJmIMkIuK0XazfnI677oV
